text: Parvati Shallow is an American yoga instructor, life speaker, charity organizer, and reality television personal. She is best know for her time on Survivor where She was the winner of Survivor Fans vs Favorites. She also completed in Survivor Cook Islands where she got 6th place, Survivor heros vs villains where she was the runner up and Survivor winners at war where she got 16th place.
